Spined boots are a member-only piece of Ranged armour. A player does not require any stats or need any quests completed in order to wear the boots or gloves, unlike the other pieces of the Spined armour set.

To obtain spined boots, either receive them as a drop from spined Dagannoths or trade with another player. The player does not need to wear the boots along with the other pieces of the Spined armour set to have an honorific added to their Fremennik name in Rellekka. These boots can be stored in the armour case of a costume room, as part of the Spined armour set. Ultimate Ironmen will be unable to retrieve individual pieces until the full set is stored.
